name: Its Lie
description:
Everybody says you've went
Everybody says you are not here
Everybody's says that again, you've broken my missing heart
That's a lie...
 
How could you put me on this situation
How close you are to stars, but far from me
Everybody says you've went, but I said that's a lie
 
Everybody says that's stange
If I will wait for you
All of their words are lie
I'll be waiting for you forever
 
Without you and your name my darling
Its so dark and silent here
But that's alright
My heart is so patient
Patient...
